[MUSIC PLAYING]

Introducing the Juice Fountain Cold by Breville. With cold spin technology and a supersize jug, you can produce to up to twice the amount of nutrient rich juice in just a fraction of the time. Let's see it in action. Juice more, store more, clean less. The Juice Fountain Cold brought to you by the food thinkers of Breville.
